# Deployment Configuration

## Docker

[Dockerfile](mdc:Dockerfile) defines the container image for the CV application.

**Best Practices:**
- Keep images minimal and secure
- Use appropriate base images
- Verify builds succeed after dependency changes

## Kubernetes & Helm

Helm charts are located in `helm/cv/`:
- `Chart.yaml` - Chart metadata
- `values.yaml` - Default configuration values
- `templates/` - Kubernetes resource templates

**Guidelines:**
- Follow Kubernetes naming conventions
- Use appropriate resource limits
- Document configuration changes
- Run `helm lint` after changes to validate
- Follow Kubernetes best practices for services and deployments

## Configuration Management

- Keep sensitive data out of version control
- Use ConfigMaps and Secrets appropriately
- Document any environment-specific settings
